### Request API Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/request-api

### Get All Open Requests (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/request-api/open-requests

### Get Request Details by Number (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/request-api/request/REQ-2026-00001

### Create Blood Request
POST http://localhost:5000/request-api/create-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

{
  "patientName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "patientAge": 45,
  "patientGender": "MALE",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "unitsRequired": 2,
  "hospitalName": "Apollo Hospital",
  "hospitalAddress": "Banjara Hills, Hyderabad",
  "state": "Telangana",
  "contactPerson": "Dr. Anita Rao",
  "contactNumber": "9876543210",
  "alertLevel": "RED",
  "requiredByDate": "2026-07-10"
}

### Get My Requests
GET http://localhost:5000/request-api/my-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

### Edit Blood Request
PUT http://localhost:5000/request-api/edit-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001",
  "patientName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "patientAge": 46,
  "patientGender": "MALE",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "unitsRequired": 3,
  "hospitalName": "Apollo Hospital",
  "hospitalAddress": "Banjara Hills, Hyderabad",
  "state": "Telangana",
  "contactPerson": "Dr. Anita Rao",
  "contactNumber": "9876543210",
  "alertLevel": "RED",
  "requiredByDate": "2026-07-10"
}

### Close Blood Request
PATCH http://localhost:5000/request-api/close-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001"
}

### Delete Blood Request (soft delete)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/request-api/delete-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001"
}

### Requester Dashboard
GET http://localhost:5000/request-api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

### Confirm Donation (Requester confirms a donor actually donated)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/request-api/confirm-donation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REQUESTER_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001",
  "donorId": "DONOR_OBJECT_ID_HERE"
}
